const aboutText = {
    professional:
        "Since 2020, I have been working in web development"
        + "\n"
        + "to advance and switch my career from teaching."
        + "\n"
        + "Since then, my main project was a career exploration"
        + "\n"
        + "app (GoPuruse) that I built entirely from the ground up."
        + "\nPrior to this, I worked as a teacher for the past 10+ years."
        + "\nI have experience with JS, React, Ruby/Rails, Python/Django, \nand HTML/CSS.",
    personal:
        "I live in DC with my girlfriend and two dachshunds."
        + "\nIn my free time, I like to work on and listen"
        + "\ninto music, exercise, and explore the city.",
};

export default aboutText;
